snippet.title: Gnomitaire Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Gnomitaire is a tiny Solitaire for clever Gnomes.

Take a seat in Card Crawl's cozy tavern and play a round of Gnomitaire with your favorite Barkeeper. In this original solitaire style card game you order 16 randomly generated cards into 4 columns by matching the correct card types.

Download on the App Store: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/id1526477736
and Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.tinytouchtales.gnomitaire

Design & Code by Arnold Rauers (Tinytouchtales)
Art & Animation by Max Fiedler
Music & Sound by Oliver Salkic
Additional Code by Will Hankinson
